getNumCells

public int getNumCells()
Return the number of cells on the array. This is the number of the intensity data elements and is == getRows() * getCols() Stdev, NumPixels, Outlier and Masked data is optional, but if present they will have getNumCells elements.

Returns:
Number of cells in the array.
